profile_positions.description:
Main Project features: Training Content and Manual Development, Capacity Development.
Activities performed:
-	Developing training content and manual in English for professional training on “Application of Geographical Information System (GIS)”;
-	Conducting training sessions as Co-Trainer;
-	Evaluating the performance of participants;
-	Preparing training completion report and submitted to BIP

Main Project features: Prepared Master Plan, GPS Survey, Topographic Survey, Data Analysis and Compilation report, Prepared Report.
Activities performed:
-	Prepare operational guidelines (OG) for preparation and implementation of Upazila and Paurashava Governance Improvement Plan (GIP), as a part of Master Plan.
-	Prepare monitoring and evaluation reports based on information obtained from different levels of project implementation;
-	Provide support in organizing workshops, seminars, conferences, dialogues and other interventions in terms of material preparation, logistical arrangements, collection and dissemination of relevant information;
-	Internal and external communication of the project with stakeholders.
